{"tw": {"3150510": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Humiliation Dungeon Survivors", "steam_appid": 3150510, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《凌辱地牢的倖存者》是一款2.5D的倖存者Roguelike玩法的冒險遊戲。十多名不同職業的可愛女孩，幾十種武器與上百種道具，在這個充滿了多種魔物的危險地牢中，努力地倖存，用你的魅力將那些對你垂涎欲滴的魔物捕獲到你的榨精農場中，用你的身體為女神收集許多的魔物精粹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果不小心受到特殊魔物的攻擊，她們將會遭受無情的凌辱！成功進行QTE來脫逃！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她們的衣服將在受到傷害時逐漸溶解…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凌辱過你的怪物都可以被捕捉到你的農場中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d06e5c6b906e2bad321aa2320eb144e7.avif?t=1772697541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras_big/d06e5c6b906e2bad321aa2320eb144e7.avif?t=1772697541 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用他們來獲得更多的魔物精粹吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/19ab8beed0ac1195f010885948b6d3f5.avif?t=1772697541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras_big/19ab8beed0ac1195f010885948b6d3f5.avif?t=1772697541 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >購買獨特的戰鬥道具來改變角色的造型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=272 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨機生成的地牢、豐富的武器與道具、各式各樣的敵人，增加可玩性與策略性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=640 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425b