<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["Naku Kinoko"], "publishers": ["Naku Kinoko"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 18, "description": "部分控制器支援"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "2", "description": "策略"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 3 月 20 日"}}}}, "us": {"3150510": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Humiliation Dungeon Survivors", "steam_appid": 3150510, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/1425bdd0d59d925f40149740acf8bad8.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survivors of the Humiliation Dungeon is a 2.5D survivor-style roguelike adventure game. Over a dozen cute girls of different professions, dozens of weapons, and hundreds of items—survive in this dangerous dungeon filled with monsters. Use your charm to capture the lustful monsters into your semen farm, and collect their essence for the goddess with your body!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/6b29973c03f64d1b7bf6da66cf6a770a.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If attacked by special monsters, they will suffer relentless humiliation! Escape by successfully completing QTEs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/36a8672e1d0553cd45b6a441cfb6a21b.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their clothes will gradually dissolve as they take damage…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/cf44a615a9c4f7a8ac78312d0f1a7ff8.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters that humiliate you can be captured in your farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d06e5c6b906e2bad321aa2320eb144e7.avif?t=1772697541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras_big/d06e5c6b906e2bad321aa2320eb144e7.avif?t=1772697541 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use them to obtain more monster essence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/19ab8beed0ac1195f010885948b6d3f5.avif?t=1772697541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras_big/19ab8beed0ac1195f010885948b6d3f5.avif?t=1772697541 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase unique combat items to change your character’s appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.poster.avif?t=1772697541\" width=272 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.webm?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150510/extras/d63163f787bd2a500e305432ee8356b4.mp4?t=1772697541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated dungeons, a variety of weapons a